No way, Daniella. No way!

927
01:08:33,704 --> 01:08:38,266
[ Daniella On Tape ]
Oh, my God! No, Max! Please stop!

928
01:08:38,342 --> 01:08:41,368
- [ Max On Tape ] I'm gonna kill you!
- Police?.

929
