953
01:10:15,372 --> 01:10:18,170
I'm innocent! I'm innocent!

954
01:10:18,242 --> 01:10:20,301
- [ Gavel Rapping]
- Claude!

955
01:10:20,377 --> 01:10:23,540
Claude, I beg of you!
Please stop this!

956
01:10:23,614 --> 01:10:26,606
Tell them I didn't do it!
Tell them I'm innocent!

957
